sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Script1 as build_engineering_state_from_step.py
    participant Reader as StepReader
    participant Builder as StepToEngineeringStateBuilder
    participant Svc as EngineeringStateService
    participant FS as outputs/iki1602

    User->>Script1: python build_engineering_state_from_step.py IKI1602.STEP
    Script1->>Reader: parse(step_path)
    Reader->>Reader: 词法解析 ISO-10303-21 + 几何抽取
    Reader-->>Script1: StepParseResult(bbox_mm, part_count, cylinders[])
    Script1->>Builder: build(project_id, result, step_path)
    Builder->>Builder: 同轴分桶聚类圆柱 → Joints (OQ6)
    Builder->>Builder: 默认铝/钢 Materials + 默认热耗 ThermalLoads (OQ1)
    Builder-->>Script1: EngineeringState(revision=1, unresolved=1)
    Script1->>Svc: put(state, expected_revision=0)
    Svc-->>Script1: EngineeringState(revision=1)
    Script1->>FS: write engineering-state.json

    Note over User,FS: ===== 特性一 · 第二脚本（几何交接） =====
    actor User2
    participant Script2 as build_spaceclaim_handoff.py
    participant Compiler as SpaceClaimHandoffCompiler
    participant Renderer as SpaceClaimV251Renderer
    User2->>Script2: python build_spaceclaim_handoff.py
    Script2->>Svc: get(project_id, revision=1)
    Svc-->>Script2: EngineeringState
    Script2->>Compiler: compile(state)
    Compiler->>Compiler: 推导 segment_angle_deg=360 & fins 默认 (OQ3)
    Compiler->>Compiler: Material→MaterialProperties 补缺 8 字段 (OQ5)
    Compiler->>Compiler: 派生 named_selections / contacts / output_plan
    Compiler-->>Script2: SpaceClaimHandoffContract(approval_status=approved)
    Script2->>FS: write spaceclaim-handoff.json
    Script2->>Renderer: write(handoff, workspace)
    Renderer-->>Script2: outputs/iki1602/spaceclaim-handoff.py

    Note over User,FS: ===== 特性二 · PDF 预提取 → 知识库（幂等） =====
    actor User3
    participant Script3 as seed_knowledge_base.py / PDF 管线
    participant Ext as PdfExtractor
    participant Tpl as Templates
    participant Lib as KnowledgeLibrary
    User3->>Script3: 传入 PDF 或执行 seed
    Script3->>Ext: extract(pdf_path)
    Ext->>Tpl: 套 MotorDatasheetTemplate / RobotArmSpecTemplate
    Tpl-->>Ext: 结构化字段（低置信 → needs_review, OQ7）
    Ext->>Lib: upsert_motor / upsert_material (content_hash 幂等)
    Lib-->>Ext: 已存在则跳过
    Ext-->>Script3: DocEntry(status)
